longBusinessSummary: Nordicus Partners Corporation provides financial consulting services to Nordic companies. It offers services in the areas of business valuation, growth strategy and budgeting, investment memorandum, business capital attracting, reverse takeover, company acquisitions and sale, green energy/clean tech, life science, e-commerce, blockchain, and SaaS. The company was formerly known as EKIMAS Corporation and changed its name to Nordicus Partners Corporation in May 2023. Nordicus Partners Corporation was founded in 1993 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
